<title>CANADA: CBRS raises Abitibi-Price rating, outlook.</title>
<headline>CBRS raises Abitibi-Price rating, outlook.</headline>
<dateline>MONTREAL 1996-08-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>Canadian Bond Rating Service on Wednesday said it upgraded the rating on Abitibi-Price's commercial paper to A-2(High) from A-2 and revised its rating outlook on the company to positive from stable.</p>
<p>The debt rating agency also reaffirmed the ratings of the company's senior unsecured debentures and preferred shares at B++(Low) and P-3(Low) respectively.</p>
</text>
